{"tid":2096090,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"法國網絡安全部門：不會全禁華為 但會敦促唔好用","createTime":"2020-07-06T02:24:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-06T03:58:20.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0f380da88d913e985e7f74f9b331ffb6b9e03ff2","tid":2096090,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T02:24:41.000Z","msg":"法國網絡安全機構部門表示，法國在推出5G電信網絡的過程中，不會全面禁止使用中國電信設備生產商華為的設備，或阻止華為參與當地的5G網絡建設，不過，會敦促法國的電訊公司，若果未有使用華為設備的話，要盡量避免使用。<br />\n<br />\n法國國家網絡安全局負責人普帕爾強調，法國的決定並非對中國存在敵意，亦不是針對華為，只是認為使用歐洲或非歐洲供應商的時候，存在不同的風險。<br />\n<br />\n法國主要電訊商Orange，已經決定選擇使用歐洲電訊設備商諾基亞及愛立信作為5G合作伙伴。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1535980-20200706.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1535980-20200706.htm&d=HclisOHeH6vmzOJk9j96FnyU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=90551365\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1535980-20200706.htm&h=a1f8d562\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1535980-20200706.htm</a>"},{"pid":"6aab486a617c605165149b9656cfb9f82be517d4","tid":2096090,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T02:44:53.000Z","msg":"禁咪禁囉  法國佬咁撚驚做乜鳩  全世界都話禁  好心佢就跟機啦屌佢老歐洲病夫"},{"pid":"9f6a4f1cda11eef78d462d1880843fa653b1be78","tid":2096090,"uid":27146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T03:56:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BN7Ore8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBN7Ore8.jpg&h=2563f1bb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bbb5c8b1f08e0ed58fcd5516b3f7f8199a233162","tid":2096090,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T03:58:20.000Z","msg":"其實咁樣已經夠,費事啲左膠又話歧視"}]}